      "Wa-yan-sou-ra-kal-laa-hou-nas-ran-'a-ZEE-ZAA",
      "Hou-wal-la-dhee-an-za-las-sa-kee-na-ta-fee-qou-loo-bil-mou'-mi-nee-na-li-yaz-daa-doo-ee-maa-nan-ma-'a-ee-maa-ni-him-wa-lil-laa-hi-jou-noo-dus-sa-maa-waa-ti-wal-ardi-wa-kaa-nal-laa-hou-'a-lee-man-ha-KEE-MAA",
